        <mxCell id="QZNlm_UlfSd-8NdxVIhh-7" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="&lt;div&gt;- As a user, I want to view current weather so that I know the current conditions.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- As a user, I want to search weather by location so that I can check weather in different areas.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- As a user, I want to view weather forecast so that I can plan ahead.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- As an admin, I want to update weather data so that the system shows accurate information.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- As an admin, I want to delete outdated weather data so that the system remains clean.&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="240" width="520" x="160" y="1700" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="QZNlm_UlfSd-8NdxVIhh-8" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="&lt;div&gt;Create:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- Add weather data&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Read:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- View weather information&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Update:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- Update weather data&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Delete:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- Delete outdated weather data&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Search:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- Search weather by location&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="230" width="600" x="80" y="1990" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="QZNlm_UlfSd-8NdxVIhh-9" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="&lt;div&gt;| Field&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; | Description |&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;|------------------|------------|&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;| Use Case ID&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; | W-01 |&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;| Use Case Name&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; | View Weather Information |&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;| Description&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; | This use case allows the user to view weather information for a specific location. |&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;| Actor&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; | User |&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;| Trigger&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; | User enters a location and clicks &quot;Search&quot;. |&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;| Precondition&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;| Weather data exists in the system. |&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;| Postcondition&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; | Weather information is displayed to the user. |&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;| Main Flow&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; | 1. User enters location. &amp;lt;br&amp;gt;2. User clicks search. &amp;lt;br&amp;gt;3. System retrieves weather data. &amp;lt;br&amp;gt;4. System displays weather information. |&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;| Alternative Flow | A1: Location not found &amp;lt;br&amp;gt;1. System displays error message. |&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="442" width="540" x="150" y="2320" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
